          mandatory="true"
          multi-select="false"
          show-field-help="true"
        >
          <label id="Question.Label.R2">R2. Household has previously received CPS (voluntary/ court ordered)</label>
          <help-text id="Question.Help.R2">Count prior investigations involving any adult members of the current household who are alleged perpetrators. Do not count prior investigations in which allegations were perpetrated by an adult who does not currently live in the household. Do not answer 'YES' if household has received CPS prior to the investigation resulting in the current case. Service history includes voluntary or court-ordered family services or Family Preservation Services but does not include delinquency services.</help-text>
        </question>
      </cluster>
