          <label id="Question.Label.R8">R8. Primary caregiver has/had a mental health problem</label>
          <help-text id="Question.Help.R8">Answer 'Yes' if credible and/or verifiable statements by the primary caregiver or others indicate that the primary caregiver:&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; Has been diagnosed with a Diagnostic and Statistical Manual (DSM) condition by a mental health clinician;&lt;li&gt; Had repeated referrals for mental health/psychological evaluations; or&lt;li&gt; Was recommended for treatment/hospitalization or treated/hospitalized for emotional problems at any time.&lt;/ul&gt;</help-text>
        </question>
